I have decided to switch to homemade #laundrydetergent. 
Why? Well, a few reasons….
1. Cost. 
2. Ingredients 
3. To prevent build up in our old pipes. 
4. We’ve been struggling with random ‘oil’ buildup spots on our clothes that then need scrubbing and a second wash. I’m tired of that. So we’re trying this. 

I made a double batch… but one batch is: 
1 Box Borax 
1 Box Arm & Hammer Laundry Soda 
3 Bars #felsnaptha 

➡️ P.S. I’ve switched to 1 part vinegar and 1 part water for #fabricsoftener and it’s been amazing for our machine and true softness in our clothes. 

I’ll keep you posted! 

#lanundry #Laundrytok #homemadelaundrydetergent
